com.unibeta.vrules.tools

Class Java2vRules

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.unibeta.vrules.tools.Java2vRules

  • public class Java2vRules
extends java.lang.Object
    An util vRules4j-Digester tool which is used for digesting the java object to vRules configurations. The original codes is contributed by Terry.Jiang.
    Author:
    Jordan.Xue

        public static void digest(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> mapObj,
          java.lang.String filePath,
          java.lang.Object errorObj)
                   throws java.lang.Exception
        Powers the strictest rules' configuration file via the given Map types objects, meanwhile, registering the returned error object. Digest the java class to vRuels.
        The default contexts would be the map key and object's class type.
        The default object id would be the simple class name as well.
